Steps to use this repository:
* Build and install your architecture's toolchain to a directory, referred to below as <TOOLCHAIN_DIRECTORY>. This must be an absolute path.
* Build and install your BSP to an installed BSP directory, referred to below as <BSP_DIRECTORY>. This must be an absolute path.
* Run "git submodule init"
* Run "git submodule update"
* Run "./waf configure" with the following options:
** --prefix="<BSP_DIRECTORY>"
** --rtems-tools="absolute/path/to/toolchain/directory"
* Run "./waf" to build the example binary
